Tile Loop Factory:
1. Scope: 
	a. Levels: 2 Common levels + 1 Bonus round 
2. Core loop
	a. Tap tile to move it to available slot in holding tray
	b. GameOver when jamming all slots
	c. Win level on clear all the tile
3. Bonus level: 
	a. start when finish the 2nd level.
	b. One click button to sequence clear all titles
	
	
	

	